text: Gumerovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kadyrgulovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 40 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 44 km from Davlekanovo, 3 km from Kadyrgulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Gumerovo, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
